PHASE*.md
*_SUMMARY.md
*_TESTING.md
test_*.py
!tests/test_*.py
docs/development/plan.md
docs/development/*_OLD.md
docs/development/BUGFIX_*.md
docs/development/CACHE.md
docs/development/IMPLEMENTATION_*.md
